    <data key="d0">LeasePlan: Leverages Serverless to Increase Driver Safety Reduce Fleet Costs and Lower Risk</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QOtCpD23118</data>
    <data key="d2">OneConnect ingests vehicle telematics to score driver safety. Scales processing and increases durability using SQS, and optimizes map queries by pre-chunking OpenStreetMaps data into 1-degree chunks.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion,interactive,compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
